snippet.title: Violet Storm for iOS Preview - Coming March 29
snippet.description: Hi. :) This is a quick preview of our upcoming all-out, neon-glow space shooter Violet Storm for iOS. Check out http://www.sadcatsoft.com/vs/main.php for more info and screenshots. Thanks for watching! :)
